{"title_page": "List of CBRN warfare forces", "text_new": "Several countries around the world maintain military units that are specifically trained to cope with CBRN (Chemical, Biological, Radiological, Nuclear) threats. Beside this specialized units, most modern armed forces undergo generalized basic CBRN self-defense training for all their personnel. \n\n{{TOC right}}\n==Albania==\n* Central Laboratory of the Armed Forces \u2013 Military Unit Nr.4010 ('' Laboratori Qendror i Forcave t\u00eb Armatosura - Rep. Usht. Nr.4010'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://aaf.mil.al/index.php/brigada-logjistike/159-struktura/4356-laboratori-qendror-i-forcave-te-armatosura-rep-usht-nr-4010|title=Laboratori Qendror i Forcave t\u00eb Armatosura Rep. Usht. Nr.4010|website=aaf.mil.al|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref> \n\n==Argentina==\n* 601st Chemical Biological Nuclear and Emergency Support Engineers Company (''Compa\u00f1\u00eda de Ingenieros de Defensa Quimica Bacteriologica Nuclear y Apoyo a la Emergencia 601'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.argentina.gob.ar/noticias/el-ministerio-de-defensa-visito-la-compania-de-ingenieros-de-defensa-qbn-y-apoyo-la|title=El Ministerio de Defensa visit\u00f3 la Compa\u00f1\u00eda de Ingenieros de Defensa QBN y Apoyo a la Emergencia 601, para informarse acerca del equipamiento y las capacidades de esta subunidad especial|website=argentina.gob.ar|date=16 May 2019|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Australia==\n* Special Operations Engineer Regiment<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.army.gov.au/our-people/units/special-operations-command/special-operations-engineer-regiment|title=Special Operations Engineer Regiment|website=army.gov.au|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Austria==\n* Atomic, Biological, Chemical (ABC) \u2013 Defense School \u201cLise Meitner\u201d (''Atomar, Biologisch, Chemisch (ABC)-Abwehrschule \u201cLise Meitner\u201d'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bundesheer.at/cms/artikel.php?ID=3351|title=ABC-Abwehrschule feiert neuen Traditionsnamen|website=Bundesheer.at|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n* ABC Defense Company - 3rd Headquarters Battalion  (''ABC-Abwehrkompanie - Stabsbataillon 3'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bundesheer.at/sk/lask/brigaden/pzgrenbrig3/baon/pzstb3.shtml|title=Stabsbataillon 3|website=Bundesheer.at|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n* ABC Defense Company - 4th Armored Headquarters Battalion (''ABC-Abwehrkompanie - Panzerstabsbataillon 4'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bundesheer.at/sk/lask/brigaden/pzgrenbrig4/baon/pzstb4.shtml|title=Panzerstabsbataillon 4|website=Bundesheer.at|date= |accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n* ABC Defense Company - Headquarters Battalion 3 (''ABC-Abwehrkompanie - Stabsbataillon 7'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bundesheer.at/sk/lask/brigaden/jgbrig7/baon/stbb7.shtml|title=Stabsbataillon 7|website=Bundesheer.at|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Belgium==\n* Competence Center \u2013 Engineer Department (''Centre de Comp\u00e9tence - D\u00e9partement G\u00e9nie'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mil.be/fr/unites/centre-de-competence-departement-genie|title=Centre de Comp\u00e9tence \u2013 D\u00e9partement G\u00e9nie|website=mil.be|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref> \n* Chemical Biological Radiological, Nuclear Company \u2013 4th Engineer Battalion (''Compagnie Chimique, Biologique, Radiologique, Nucl\u00e9aire - 4 Bataillon du G\u00e9nie'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mil.be/sites/mil.be/files/jobdetail/76623-en52x-f_2.pdf|title=Soldat Assistant op\u00e9rateur CBRN|website=mil.be|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Belarus==\n*Department of Radiation, Chemical and Biological (RCB) Protection and Ecology  ('' \u0423\u043f\u0440\u0430\u045e\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0435 \u0440\u0430\u0434\u044b\u044f\u0446\u044b\u0439\u043d\u0430\u0439, \u0445\u0456\u043c\u0456\u0447\u043d\u0430\u0439 i \u0431\u0456\u044f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0456\u0447\u043d\u0430\u0439 (\u0420\u0425\u0411) \u0430\u0431\u0430\u0440\u0