a'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zeniad.wordpress.com/2009/01/21/detasmen-kompi-zeni-nubika-tni-ad-atau-detasmen-kompi-pengendali-senjata-pemusnah-massal/|title=KOMPI ZENI NUBIKA TNI AD\n |website=zeniad.wordpress.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Iran==\n[[Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps]]\n* 24th Chemical Warfare Brigade \"Bessat\" <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.academia.edu/8069971/ARMED_FORCES_OF_THE_ISLAMIC_REPUBLIC_OF_IRAN|title=Armed Forces of the Islamic Republic of Iran (Chapter 3, page 38)|website=academia.edu|author=Stephen Hughes|date=|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Israel==\n* 76th Chemical Defense Battalion (''76 \u05d2\u05d3\u05d5\u05d3 \u05d4\u05e1\u05d9\u05d5\u05e2 \u05d4\u05db\u05d9\u05de\u05d9'') <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.handasa.org.il/print?c0=17700|title=\u05d2\u05d3\u05d5\u05d3 76|website=handasa.org.il|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Italy==\n* Joint Nuclear, Biological and Nuclear Defense School (''Scuola Interforze per la Difesa Nucleare, Biologica e Chimica'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.difesa.it/SMD_/EntiMI/ScuolaNBC/Pagine/default.aspx|title=Scuola Interforze per la Difesa NBC|website=Difesa.it|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n* [[7th CBRN Defense Regiment \"Cremona\"|7th Chemical, Biological, Radiological and Nuclear Defense Regiment \u201cCremona\u201d]] (''7\u00b0 Reggimento Difesa Chimica, Biologica, Radioattiva e Nucleare \u201cCremona\u201d'') <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esercito.difesa.it/organizzazione/capo-di-sme/comfoter-supporto/comando-artiglieria/7-reggimento-difesa-nbc-cremona|title=7\u00b0 Reggimento Difesa CBRN \"Cremona\"|website=esercito.difesa.it|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Japan==\n*Ground Self-Defense Force Chemical School (''\u9678\u4e0a\u81ea\u885b\u968a\u5316\u5b66\u5b66\u6821 - Rikuj\u014d Jieitai Kagaku Gakk\u014d'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shugiin.go.jp/internet/itdb_shitsumon.nsf/html/shitsumon/a184003.htm|title=\u9678\u4e0a\u81ea\u88